title: CLASH OF THE GODS - Age of Mythology: HD Edition Gameplay
description:
CLASH OF THE GODS - Age of Mythology: HD Edition Gameplay - Hey guys!  Today we have a blast from the past.  We are playing some Age of Mythology!  Heph will be joining me in todays video.  We are playing a 2v2 match against 2 medium AI.  Heph will be fighting as the Vikings under Loki and I will be fighting as the greek under Hades. Enjoy the battle :D 

Heph's Channel: https://www.youtube.com/user/Hephaestionn

****You can support my channel now by buying a game from White Tie Games using this link: https://www.whitetiegames.com/affiliates/ref?pr=cd4380&type=main

If you enjoyed the video don't forget to Like and Leave a comment :D
